      <title>由于中国和美国电动汽车的增长，今年汽油需求增长将放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gasoline-demand-growth-slow-this-year-ev-growth-china-us-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，受中国和美国转向电动汽车以及去年 COVID-19 疫情爆发后恢复正常消费的推动，全球汽油需求增长可能会在 2024 年减半，从而挤压下半年炼油厂的利润率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gasoline-demand-growth-slow-this-year-ev-growth-china-us-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:23:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
